<item>
            <title>[ZOOKEEPER-808] Web-based Administrative Interface</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/ZOOKEEPER-808</link>
                <project id="12310801" key="ZOOKEEPER">ZooKeeper</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Implement a web-based administrative interface that should allow the user to perform all the tasks that can be done using the interactive shell (zkCli.sh) from a browser. It should also display cluster and individual server info extracted using the 4letter word commands. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;m going to build starting from the &lt;a href=&quot;http://github.com/phunt/zookeeper_dashboard&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow&quot;&gt;http://github.com/phunt/zookeeper_dashboard&lt;/a&gt; implemented by Patrick Hunt. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
